# LeetCode #412: Fizz Buzz
# Count from 1 to 15. For multiples of 3 say "Fizz", multiples of 5
# say "Buzz", multiples of both say "FizzBuzz".

for each n from 1 to 15
    if n is divisible by 15 then
        print "FizzBuzz"
    otherwise if n is divisible by 3 then
        print "Fizz"
    otherwise if n is divisible by 5 then
        print "Buzz"
    otherwise
        print n
    end
end
